sect1.title: External Interfaces
sect1.para: The external interfaces are represented by the generated RTE based on the DWAX_SstSr.xml sst file. DWAX_SstSr.xml is exported from DWA_SST.xlsx with the mapping set in the DWAX_SstSr.xsd file.

DWAX_SST.xlsx location: https://github-vni.geo.conti.de/bs-vw-meb-19-icas1-chorus/sw.sys.chorus_main_doc/tree/master/mc_sw/appl/DWASensorSirene/DWAX/c/cfg/sst/DWAX_SST.xlsx DWAX_SstSr.xsd location: https://github-vni.geo.conti.de/bs-vw-meb-19-icas1-chorus/sw.sys.chorus_main_doc/blob/master/mc_sw/appl/DWASensorSirene/DWAX/c/cfg/rteCfg/xsd/DWAX_SstSr.xsd DWAX_SstSr.xml location: https://github-vni.geo.conti.de/bs-vw-meb-19-icas1-chorus/sw.sys.chorus_main_doc/blob/master/mc_sw/appl/DWASensorSirene/DWAX/c/cfg/rteLight/mirror/DWAX_SstSr.xml

sect1.title: External Dependencies
sect1.para: DWAX component has no external dependencies because acts like a wrapper for DWA.
